            "body": "<p>Example how to detect 2nd Monday<\/p>\n<pre><code>val DateTime.is2ndMonday\n    get() = dayOfWeek == 1 &amp;&amp; dayOfMonth &gt; 7\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
